4. TIER GATING (PATREON ENTITLEMENT)

The Software offers a free tier and one or more paid tiers. Paid
tiers unlock additional features through an entitlement check
against an active Patreon pledge to Licensor's campaign. You agree
that:

  (a) the entitlement check is part of the Software and may not be
      bypassed, modified, or stubbed;
  (b) tier feature lists may change as the Software evolves;
      Licensor will not retroactively reduce features on a tier
      that a User has already paid for during the period that
      pledge is active, but reserves the right to add new features
      to higher tiers without obligation to backport;
  (c) cancellation of a Patreon pledge results in the Software
      reverting to the free tier on the next entitlement refresh
      (typically within 6 hours).

5. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES

The Software integrates with third-party services including but
not limited to Twitch, YouTube, Kick, TikTok (via TikFinity),
Discord, Patreon, Cloudflare, Spotify, OBS, and Streamer.bot. Your
use of those services is governed by their own terms; Licensor is
not responsible for the availability, reliability, or behaviour of
third-party services.

6. DATA + PRIVACY

The Software stores configuration and operational data locally on
your device. Off-stream features (Discord bot wallet, viewer
profile editing) store data in Cloudflare KV under per-streamer
HMAC-gated keys. Patreon OAuth tokens are stored locally and
exchanged with Patreon only via a Cloudflare Worker proxy
controlled by Licensor. Licensor does not sell, share, or
otherwise transmit your personal data except as needed to operate
the Software's documented features.

